♪ Tossed salads
and scrambled eggs ♪

21:31.590 --> 21:33.392
♪ Oh, my ♪

21:33.392 --> 21:34.893
♪ And maybe
I seem a bit confused ♪

21:34.893 --> 21:38.397
♪ Well, maybe,
but I got you pegged ♪

21:38.397 --> 21:39.865
(laughing)

21:39.865 --> 21:41.900
♪ But I don't know
what to do ♪

21:41.900 --> 21:46.271
♪ With those tossed salads
and scrambled eggs ♪

21:46.271 --> 21:49.408
♪ They're callin' again. ♪

21:49.408 --> 21:52.544
Thank you!

